Package com.example.project3

package com.example.project3
  • Class
    Description
    Account
    Account class is the parent class of Savings, Money Market, Checking, and College Checking classes
    AccountDatabase
    Account Database performs the actions on the array of accounts (i.e open, close, find, sort, etc.)
    Campus
    Enum class for campuses New Brunswick, Newark, and Camden
    Checking
    Extends the Account class and is used to create a Checking account
    CollegeChecking
    Extends the Checking class and is used to create a College Checking account
    Date
    Writing our own Date class to initialize dates and check for validity
    MoneyMarket
    Money Market is an extension of Savings account class, has more benefits and costs
    Profile
    Holds the identity of holders Includes first name, last name, and date of birth
    Savings
    Savings is an extension of the parent Account class
    TransactionManagerController
    Transaction Manager Controller contains the button click actions and functionality of our Transaction Manager GUI These functionalities include opening, closing, depositing, withdrawing from accounts, cancel and clear buttons, etc.
    TransactionManagerMain
    Transaction Manager Main that launches and runs the TransactionManager application
